## Install

- From git:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/alexpdev/torrentfileQt.git
cd torrentfileQt
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install .
torrentfileQt
```

- From PyPi

```bash
pip install torrentfileQt
torrentfileQt
```

> Alternatively you can download a precompiled binary from the release page.
